	dynasty=1000028394 #Ceh-Panduranga
	religion=chamic_shaivism
	culture="cham"
	martial = 9 #Exceptional military commander who successfully invaded the mighty Khmer Empire
	diplomacy = 6 #Managed alliances but was primarily a warrior-king
	intrigue = 7 #Strategic planning for the complex naval invasion of Angkor
	stewardship = 6 #Administered conquered territories for several years
	learning = 7 #Described as "well versed in all the shastra" (religious texts)
	trait = ambitious #His drive to conquer the powerful Khmer Empire
	trait = brave #Described as "full of courage" - personally led dangerous naval invasion
	trait = wrathful #The aggressive ferocity of his invasion and sack of Angkor
	trait = arrogant #Described as "full of pride" - fits his bold conquest attempt
	trait = scholar #"Well versed in all the shastra" - knowledgeable in religious texts
	disallow_random_traits = yes
	father=1000080044
	1121.1.1={
		birth="1121.1.1"
	}
	1170.1.1 = {
		add_pressed_claim = title:e_kambujadesa #To push his historical conquest
		add_pressed_claim = title:c_aninditapura
	}

		death = yes
	}

	dynasty_house = house_kalyani_chalukya
	religion = "shaivism"
	culture = "kannada"
	martial = 9 #Excellent military commander who expanded territories significantly
	diplomacy = 7 #Managed complex coalitions with Pamplona against common enemies
	intrigue = 6 #Navigated complex political situations with multiple rival powers
	stewardship = 8 #Successfully consolidated control over various territories and provinces
	trait = ambitious #Described as "ambitious warrior" even as a prince during father's reign
	trait = brave #Poet Ranna compared him to Bhima for his "strength and valor" in battle
	trait = diligent #His effective administration and territorial consolidation efforts
	trait = scholar #His patronage of great Kannada poet Ranna and cultural contributions
	disallow_random_traits = yes
	father = 74437
	955.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	1008.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}

	name = "Jayavarman" #Jayavarman VII
	dynasty_house = house_Mahidhar
	religion = "shaivism"
	culture = "khmer"
	martial = 9 #Exceptional military leader who defeated Cham invaders and expanded empire to greatest extent
	diplomacy = 8 #Successfully unified fragmented kingdoms and managed complex political alliances
	intrigue = 6 #Politically astute but preferred direct action
	stewardship = 10 #Outstanding administrator who rebuilt empire's infrastructure and economy
	trait = ambitious #His massive territorial expansion and unprecedented building projects
	trait = diligent #His extensive administrative work and construction projects showing incredible work ethic
	trait = compassionate #Built 102 hospitals and 121 rest houses for people's welfare - centered rule on serving subjects
	trait = administrator #His excellent organizational skills in rebuilding and managing the vast empire
	trait = architect #His massive temple and infrastructure building projects including Angkor Thom and Bayon
	disallow_random_traits = yes
	father = 420031
	1153.1.1 = { #fictional date
		birth = yes
		effect = {
			add_character_flag = has_regnal_name
		}
	}
	1181.1.1 = {
		religion = "theravada" #Converted to Buddhism when he became king
		add_trait = zealous #His fervent promotion of Buddhism as state religion, breaking 400 years of Hindu tradition
	}
	1218.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}

fugu_she_003 = { #折從遠 She Congyuan or 折從阮 She Congruan. Third son of She Silun. (全唐文/卷993/刺史折嗣祚碑) Made 府州刺史 in 同光 era. (舊五代史/卷125) In 912 made 府州刺史 [possibly an error and it was Silun who was made the prefect as Congyuan was only 23 then]. (資治通鑑/卷284) 府州刺史 in 944.6.28. (資治通鑑/卷284) In 944.7.10 made 府州團練使 after leading a successful rebellion against Khitans in this area. (資治通鑑/卷284) Later made 朔州刺史、安北都護、振武軍節度使. (舊五代史/卷125) 振武節度使 in 945.3.9. (資治通鑑/卷284) 振武節度使、府州團練使 until 947.5.2, on that day made 永安軍節度使，行府州刺史 and changed name to 折從阮. (舊五代史/卷99 and 資治通鑑/卷284) In 949.11.13 made 岐國公. (舊五代史/卷102) 府州節度使 until 950.4.22, on that day made 鄧州節度使. (舊五代史/卷103 and 資治通鑑/卷289) 鄧州節度使 until 951.5.21, on that day made 滑州節度使. (舊五代史/卷111) 滑州節度使 until 951.9.26, on that day made 陜州節度使. (舊五代史/卷111) 陜州節度使 until 952.12.8, on that day made 邠州節度使. (舊五代史/卷112 and 資治通鑑/卷291) In 954.2.15 made 鄭國公. (舊五代史/卷113) 靜難節度使 until 954. (舊五代史/卷125) Former 邠州節度使 in 956.1.8, on that day died. (舊五代史/卷115)

(續資治通鑑長編/卷128) 責鄜延蕃官洛苑副使 until 1046.12.6, on that day made 太子右內率府副率、京西監當. (續資治通鑑長編/卷159) Later granted name 劉紹能. (宋史/卷350) 洛苑使、英州刺史 until 1073.5.31, on that day made 鄜延路都監. (續資治通鑑長編/卷244)
